# read data from csv file
    data = pd.read_csv(csv_file_path, delimiter="\t")

    corr = data.corr()

    corr = corr.apply(pd.Series).round(2)

    heatmap = sns.heatmap(
        corr,
        cmap="RdYlGn",

    )

    ax.set_title(title)
    return corr, heatmap
